original_title: 女陰陽師 邪淫覚醒
overview: Idol Lulu begins to feel danger for herself. At that time, disturbing clouds swirling in the sky of Akihabara... Araki was performing a ritual to revive the evil god Arahabaki. For that purpose, the power of Lulu, who was a female Onmyouji 1000 years ago, was indispensable! Now is the time to protect the world as a female Onmyoji!
title: Woman Onmyoji Awakening of Perversion
